Detailed Description

The Parameters for a capability. Parameters can be everything that describes a capability. A MakeCoffeeCapability for example might have the following parameters:

struct Parameters : public Capability::Parameters {
enum Strength {
Light,
Medium,
Strong
};
Strength strength;
bool with_milk;
int number_of_sugar_cubes;
};
